1
00:00:07,220 --> 00:00:11,820
♪She looks at the bright moon
hanging high above the clouds♪

2
00:00:11,860 --> 00:00:14,140
♪And I fall into the mountains♪

3
00:00:14,220 --> 00:00:16,100
♪Protect this broken world♪

4
00:00:16,180 --> 00:00:20,620
♪A faint wish♪

5
00:00:20,660 --> 00:00:23,900
♪Life is just a dream,
isn't the world so?♪

6
00:00:23,980 --> 00:00:27,620
♪Looking back,
I count the joys of my remaining years♪

7
00:00:27,700 --> 00:00:31,020
♪It's difficult to see you in my dreams♪

8
00:00:31,060 --> 00:00:33,940
♪Ignoring the coldness of the world,
I still linger♪

9
00:00:33,980 --> 00:00:37,300
♪Love and hate are intertwined,
not just in the past♪

10
00:00:37,340 --> 00:00:40,900
♪The past is painful
and time goes by in a flash♪

11
00:00:40,940 --> 00:00:44,500
♪Stars fall on the mountain top again♪

12
00:00:44,580 --> 00:00:48,140
♪My heart is as pure as the moon
and connected to you♪

13
00:00:54,140 --> 00:00:56,980
[No One But You]

14
00:00:56,980 --> 00:00:58,700
[Episode 21]

15
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:01,980
[In the deepest abyss,
I will be there with you.]

16
00:01:26,540 --> 00:01:27,860
I didn't see you when I woke up.

17
00:01:29,540 --> 00:01:30,940
I was scared it was all just a dream.

18
00:01:39,500 --> 00:01:40,700
What about now?

19
00:01:41,180 --> 00:01:43,180
Do you still think it was just a dream?

20
00:01:43,180 --> 00:01:44,540
♪The old garden causes tears♪

21
00:01:47,580 --> 00:01:49,620
You're much more wonderful than a dream.

22
00:01:50,300 --> 00:01:51,260
For so many years,

23
00:01:52,540 --> 00:01:54,180
sometimes, I didn't even know

24
00:01:54,540 --> 00:01:55,820
if I was a human or a ghost.

25
00:01:57,380 --> 00:02:00,020
Just because you are there,

26
00:02:00,380 --> 00:02:02,980
I feel I'm alive

27
00:02:02,980 --> 00:02:04,500
♪But years have gone by♪

28
00:02:04,500 --> 00:02:06,220
and haven't turned into a ghost.

29
00:02:07,940 --> 00:02:10,420
♪Many times,
I sighed about when you were born♪

30
00:02:10,620 --> 00:02:11,660
I understand.

31
00:02:12,460 --> 00:02:13,180
Mohan,

32
00:02:13,860 --> 00:02:15,460
you will never walk alone.

33
00:02:15,460 --> 00:02:17,260
♪Old memories stir up as I still wait♪

34
00:02:17,260 --> 00:02:18,940
Even if it's the deepest abyss,

35
00:02:19,340 --> 00:02:21,140
I will be there with you.

36
00:02:22,060 --> 00:02:23,220
From now on,

37
00:02:23,460 --> 00:02:24,660
if you walk on blades,

38
00:02:24,660 --> 00:02:25,980
I'll walk with you.

39
00:02:25,980 --> 00:02:27,340
If you cross the fires,

40
00:02:27,340 --> 00:02:28,700
I will pave the way for you.

41
00:02:29,380 --> 00:02:30,660
From now on,

42
00:02:31,100 --> 00:02:32,460
we will never part in life.

43
00:02:32,820 --> 00:02:34,100
Only death will do us part.

44
00:02:34,620 --> 00:02:36,140
♪My thoughts grow thin
with petals falling♪

45
00:02:36,140 --> 00:02:37,340
With you like this,

46
00:02:39,060 --> 00:02:40,540
what more could I ask for?

47
00:02:40,540 --> 00:02:41,580
♪It is a pity
that when you were born, I was not♪

48
00:02:41,620 --> 00:02:45,700
♪My heart is for one person♪

49
00:02:46,140 --> 00:02:48,580
♪Tears fall like the rain♪

50
00:02:48,620 --> 00:02:52,660
♪Strings are broken, words are silenced,
and the wind stops♪

51
00:02:53,260 --> 00:02:55,820
♪It is a pity
that when you were born, I was not♪

52
00:02:55,940 --> 00:03:00,020
♪Szechuan Lovage grows as time goes on♪

53
00:03:00,060 --> 00:03:02,660
♪It is a pity that after we parted♪

54
00:03:02,740 --> 00:03:06,740
♪My thoughts grow thin
with petals falling♪

55
00:03:07,260 --> 00:03:09,620
♪It is a pity
that when you were born, I was not♪

56
00:03:09,620 --> 00:03:12,980
♪My heart is for one person♪

57
00:03:12,980 --> 00:03:13,700
Sir,

58
00:03:13,940 --> 00:03:15,700
there's an important document for you.

59
00:03:15,700 --> 00:03:16,540
♪Tears fall like the rain♪

60
00:03:16,620 --> 00:03:21,380
♪Strings are broken, words are silenced,
and the wind stops♪

61
00:03:22,060 --> 00:03:22,540
Sir...

62
00:03:39,420 --> 00:03:40,340
What is it?

63
00:03:41,260 --> 00:03:42,300
Good morning.

64
00:03:43,300 --> 00:03:44,380
I believe

65
00:03:44,980 --> 00:03:46,300
it's time to discuss

66
00:03:46,300 --> 00:03:47,700
our wedding arrangements.

67
00:03:52,220 --> 00:03:52,900
I...

68
00:03:54,340 --> 00:03:55,300
I just woke up.

69
00:03:56,660 --> 00:03:57,700
Let me freshen up.

70
00:03:58,260 --> 00:03:59,140
Wait for me downstairs.

71
00:04:08,780 --> 00:04:09,700
Are you crazy?

72
00:04:12,020 --> 00:04:12,780
Yes.

73
00:04:13,220 --> 00:04:14,100
I'm crazy.

74
00:04:16,860 --> 00:04:20,260
♪The sky is waiting
for the fog to clear♪

75
00:04:20,580 --> 00:04:24,260
♪Like ears waiting for an answer♪

76
00:04:24,860 --> 00:04:30,740
♪Those who can't see clearly
still struggle♪

77
00:04:40,780 --> 00:04:41,580
Mohan,

78
00:04:42,340 --> 00:04:43,500
what took you so long?

79
00:04:45,260 --> 00:04:46,500
I fell back asleep.

80
00:04:48,980 --> 00:04:51,100
According to Chinese customs,

81
00:04:51,100 --> 00:04:53,540
the eighth day of the lunar month
is a lucky day.

82
00:04:53,540 --> 00:04:54,740
How about

83
00:04:54,940 --> 00:04:56,860
us getting married on that day?

84
00:04:58,780 --> 00:05:00,020
That's a bit in a hurry.

85
00:05:02,140 --> 00:05:05,540
Then what do you think
about the wedding dress?

86
00:05:07,260 --> 00:05:08,540
As long as you are happy.

87
00:05:10,340 --> 00:05:11,340
Then,

88
00:05:11,980 --> 00:05:15,260
should we go for the Chinese
or Japanese style?

89
00:05:16,180 --> 00:05:17,060
Whichever you want.

90
00:05:17,740 --> 00:05:18,660
Don't stress about it.

91
00:05:18,660 --> 00:05:19,740
Have some tea.

92
00:05:26,260 --> 00:05:27,900
Who are you to jump in?

93
00:05:42,340 --> 00:05:43,620
Apologize to Chihoko.

94
00:05:44,700 --> 00:05:46,340
Why should I?

95
00:05:46,460 --> 00:05:47,860
She hit me first.

96
00:05:49,940 --> 00:05:51,860
I've been too lenient with you.

97
00:05:52,180 --> 00:05:53,500
You're getting bolder.

98
00:05:54,340 --> 00:05:55,940
I really should punish you.

99
00:05:56,860 --> 00:05:57,860
I'll say it again.

100
00:05:57,860 --> 00:05:58,980
Apologize now.

101
00:05:59,260 --> 00:06:00,820
I've had enough!

102
00:06:00,820 --> 00:06:02,060
Just kill me!

103
00:06:02,540 --> 00:06:03,100
Enough.

104
00:06:03,740 --> 00:06:04,420
Mohan,

105
00:06:05,220 --> 00:06:06,940
why bother to get angry with her?

106
00:06:07,300 --> 00:06:08,820
We have important things to discuss.

107
00:06:08,820 --> 00:06:09,660
No.

108
00:06:10,380 --> 00:06:12,180
I must punish her today.

109
00:06:12,820 --> 00:06:13,660
Wait for me.

110
00:06:20,420 --> 00:06:21,120
[On Lok Yuen]

111
00:06:21,460 --> 00:06:22,780
Isn't the food here nice?

112
00:06:23,820 --> 00:06:24,900
We just left like that.

113
00:06:24,900 --> 00:06:25,980
What about Chihoko?

114
00:06:26,380 --> 00:06:28,260
It's fine. Shen Jun is with her.

115
00:06:28,260 --> 00:06:29,980
Stuffed tigers. Check these out.

116
00:06:31,740 --> 00:06:33,460
Look, it's pretty over there.

117
00:06:37,420 --> 00:06:38,460
You're annoying.

118
00:06:39,620 --> 00:06:40,300
Annoying.

119
00:06:40,300 --> 00:06:41,100
All right.

120
00:06:41,420 --> 00:06:42,180
I'll give you one.

121
00:06:42,180 --> 00:06:42,980
Just one.

122
00:06:46,420 --> 00:06:47,420
I'm sorry.

123
00:06:54,370 --> 00:06:56,940
[Yuxuan]

124
00:06:56,940 --> 00:07:02,860
♪Flowers fall into a courtyard pool,
only a few begonias blooming♪

125
00:07:04,620 --> 00:07:07,780
♪I play the guzheng under the moon,
remembering when he wrote his poems♪

126
00:07:07,780 --> 00:07:09,460
Do you believe in these vows?

127
00:07:11,140 --> 00:07:12,860
What these people wish for

128
00:07:13,300 --> 00:07:15,500
is nothing but to find a good match.

129
00:07:16,740 --> 00:07:17,980
But I've found mine.

130
00:07:19,780 --> 00:07:21,220
I'm not a good one for you.

131
00:07:21,220 --> 00:07:23,820
♪The hidden meaning in each line
drew me into the play♪

132
00:07:23,820 --> 00:07:24,620
Qinghuan,

133
00:07:26,740 --> 00:07:29,100
I don't believe in deities or ghosts.

134
00:07:29,380 --> 00:07:30,420
I don't pray.

135
00:07:31,380 --> 00:07:32,300
My only wish is

136
00:07:32,700 --> 00:07:33,820
that in the next life,

137
00:07:34,220 --> 00:07:35,580
I can be your good match.

138
00:07:35,580 --> 00:07:37,020
♪This old dream locks away
the memories of a past life♪

139
00:07:37,140 --> 00:07:39,500
♪Awakening, I open the window
but don't see you anywhere♪

140
00:07:39,500 --> 00:07:40,420
Let's get one as well.

141
00:07:40,900 --> 00:07:41,300
Okay.

142
00:07:41,300 --> 00:07:43,700
♪Rain falls on the begonias,
stirring thoughts of longing♪

143
00:07:43,940 --> 00:07:47,460
♪No one knows how much I miss you♪

144
00:07:47,820 --> 00:07:51,340
♪The wind from my hometown
does not come too late♪

145
00:07:51,500 --> 00:07:54,940
♪Yet the letter from afar
has not arrived♪

146
00:07:55,420 --> 00:07:58,620
♪If we hadn't met and known each other♪

147
00:07:58,820 --> 00:08:00,420
♪I wouldn't have been troubled by love♪

148
00:08:00,420 --> 00:08:01,020
Done.

149
00:08:01,020 --> 00:08:03,100
[Jiang Mohan]

150
00:08:03,100 --> 00:08:10,060
♪I hope the wind stops
the day you return♪

151
00:08:11,180 --> 00:08:12,140
It's a pity

152
00:08:13,020 --> 00:08:14,700
that we can't hang it up there.

153
00:08:14,700 --> 00:08:17,140
♪No one knows how much I miss you♪

154
00:08:17,220 --> 00:08:20,900
♪The wind from my hometown
does not come too late♪

155
00:08:21,140 --> 00:08:24,780
♪But the letter from afar
has not arrived♪

156
00:08:25,140 --> 00:08:26,420
Let's bury it here.

157
00:08:27,100 --> 00:08:28,620
Perhaps a hundred years later,

158
00:08:29,260 --> 00:08:30,140
some couple

159
00:08:30,540 --> 00:08:31,780
will find out our story.

160
00:08:33,140 --> 00:08:39,670
♪I hope the wind stops
the day you return♪

161
00:08:40,650 --> 00:08:50,140
♪I hope the wind stops
the day you return♪

162
00:09:02,300 --> 00:09:03,780
Why hasn't the Military Governor
come back?

163
00:09:06,340 --> 00:09:09,220
Perhaps, he's preparing
a surprise for you.

164
00:09:10,420 --> 00:09:12,300
Do you even believe that yourself?

165
00:09:14,380 --> 00:09:15,260
Take me to him.

166
00:09:15,580 --> 00:09:16,660
Absolutely not.

167
00:09:17,060 --> 00:09:18,100
He asked you

168
00:09:18,100 --> 00:09:19,620
to wait for him in the mansion.

169
00:09:19,620 --> 00:09:21,420
I wouldn't dare disobey him.

170
00:09:23,020 --> 00:09:24,300
You are afraid of him,

171
00:09:24,300 --> 00:09:26,140
but you're not afraid of me?

172
00:09:26,500 --> 00:09:27,020
Lead the way.

173
00:09:38,060 --> 00:09:40,060
The lock has been out of maintenance.

174
00:09:40,220 --> 00:09:41,100
It's broken.

175
00:09:41,660 --> 00:09:42,700
It seems

176
00:09:42,940 --> 00:09:44,380
you should stay in.

177
00:09:46,620 --> 00:09:47,540
Is that so?

178
00:09:58,380 --> 00:10:01,140
What now?

179
00:10:09,300 --> 00:10:10,780
Compared to you,

180
00:10:11,540 --> 00:10:13,420
I'm more afraid
of the Military Governor.

181
00:10:23,060 --> 00:10:23,700
Don't move.

182
00:10:26,060 --> 00:10:26,460
Move.

183
00:10:28,540 --> 00:10:29,300
Mohan!

184
00:10:31,300 --> 00:10:32,700
Chu Yunfan, are you mad?

185
00:10:33,100 --> 00:10:34,260
What are you doing?

186
00:10:34,460 --> 00:10:35,460
What am I doing?

187
00:10:35,940 --> 00:10:37,420
You killed my men.

188
00:10:37,420 --> 00:10:38,420
What do you think I'm doing?

189
00:10:38,420 --> 00:10:40,540
Fan, you can't do this.

190
00:10:40,940 --> 00:10:42,500
Don't be silly anymore.

191
00:11:02,980 --> 00:11:06,700
♪The waves♪

192
00:11:06,780 --> 00:11:10,980
♪When will you stop
looking through them?♪

193
00:11:11,060 --> 00:11:15,020
♪Missed the time
when the sun was restored♪

194
00:11:15,100 --> 00:11:19,180
♪What else do you expect to like?♪

195
00:11:19,220 --> 00:11:21,940
♪I thought you were an angel♪

196
00:11:22,020 --> 00:11:24,220
♪An angel who watched over me♪

197
00:11:24,260 --> 00:11:27,300
♪And saw every side of me♪

198
00:11:27,380 --> 00:11:29,940
♪Until reality is flooded♪

199
00:11:30,020 --> 00:11:32,180
♪You become sensible♪

200
00:11:32,260 --> 00:11:36,740
♪You are finally
out of touch with reality♪

201
00:11:37,060 --> 00:11:39,580
♪I hear the mountains, the seas,
and the people♪

202
00:11:39,660 --> 00:11:41,620
♪All clamoring because of you♪

203
00:11:41,740 --> 00:11:43,700
♪Hiding in the cape after the rain♪

204
00:11:43,860 --> 00:11:46,140
♪I cannot hear you♪

205
00:11:46,180 --> 00:11:49,660
♪So I opened my arms one last time♪

206
00:11:49,820 --> 00:11:53,180
♪But you escaped through the gap♪

207
00:11:53,300 --> 00:11:55,500
♪I saw winters come and summers go♪

208
00:11:55,540 --> 00:11:57,660
♪And thought there was ample time♪

209
00:11:57,900 --> 00:11:59,700
♪Cannot withstand the waves♪

210
00:11:59,820 --> 00:12:01,780
♪But you always make me panic♪

211
00:12:01,860 --> 00:12:06,100
♪How ridiculous, making me learn♪

212
00:12:06,180 --> 00:12:09,460
♪How much I am worth♪
